Package: consumeR
Type: Package
Title: Transparent and Reproducible Consumer Research Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
    )
Description: Provides transparent, well-documented functions for consumer research
    analysis that facilitate reproducibility during peer review. All functions are
    designed with clarity and readability in mind, making code easy to understand
    for reviewers with varying levels of programming experience. Functions include
    clear documentation, sensible defaults, and extensive examples.
